definitions.definition: A large, round, semi-permanent tent with vertical walls and a conical roof , usually associated with Central Asia and Mongolia (where it is known as a ger ).

main_definition: A large, round, semi-permanent tent with vertical walls and a conical roof , usually associated with Central Asia and Mongolia (where it is known as a ger ).

definitions.definition: The natural resources and arable land over which a Cossack stanitsa had exclusive control in their territory .

main_definition: ( historical ) The natural resources and arable land over which a Cossack stanitsa had exclusive control in their territory .
